             NYC Taxis: A Day in the Life 
             This visualization displays the data for one random NYC yellow taxi on a single day in 2013.  See where it operated, how much money it made, and how busy it was over 24 hours. Begin  
             A Special Thanks goes out to  Mapbox  and  Heroku  for assistance with covering the surge of activity when this project was first released in 2014.  
